  "method": [
    "Take a pan and heat the oil.",
    "Put onion and capsicum in a pan. Cook for 5 minutes, and stir",
    "constantly.",
    "Put cumin, garlic, and chili in it.",
    "Then add tomatoes, stock, beans, and corn. Bring it to simmer. Then",
    "lower the heat.",
    "Add lime juice, and season it with pepper and salt.",
    "Sprinkle corn chips, avocado, coriander, and fetta."
